window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Peace is earned, not given.</p> <p>Aliens are seizing planets at the edge of Berantz space. Earth Fleet sends an armada to investigate.</p> <p>They're never heard from again.</p> <p>Word reaches the Vestrall home planet of the encroachment. Declan Payne knows what has to be doneâ€”convince Leviathan to investigate. Peace through superior firepower, through the threat of annihilation.</p> <p>But Lev is retired. And so is Payne and his team.</p> <p>The choice is taken out of their hands.</p> <p>Join Declan Payne and his team as they return to a new front in a never-ending war to keep humanity safe.</p>"; 
